parameters:
【Professor Scorran】 Well, magic is classified
based on its effects.

【Professor Scorran】 In broad terms, there are
attack magic, support and healing magic, and
ritual magic.

【Professor Scorran】 Since Professor Melissa
teaches ritual magic, there's no need for an
explanation.
【Tommy】 Hmm...
【Masamune】 Is something wrong, Tommy?

【Tommy】 I'm learning a new magic, but I'm
struggling to decide what name to give it.
【Masamune】 What kind of magic is it?
【Tommy】 It's a magic that attacks with rocks.

【Masamune】 I see... In that case, how about
calling it Rock Magic?

【Tommy】 That doesn't give enough information and
it's hard to imagine.

【Tommy】 I want a name that gives the feeling of
destroying with rocks, you know?

【Masamune】 Hmm, I see... How about something like
'Impact of Rock Destruction'?
【Skeleton Head】 Heheh...
【Masamune】 Hey! You laughed, huh!

【Skeleton Head】 No, no, my bad. I think I'm cool.
Heheh...
【Masamune】 N-Na...

【Tommy】 I don't think I'm at fault either...
heheh...
【Masamune】 Even Tommy...
スキット 表情 レオン f 3
スキット スライドイン レオン f 左
【Leon】 Honestly... it's kind of lame, isn't it?
【Skeleton Head】 Hahaha...
【Masamune】 Y-You guys...

【Tommy】 Everyone, why are you laughing? I tried my
best to think of something... heheh...
【Masamune】 (I'm naturally provoking them...)
スキット 表情 レオン f 1

【Leon】 But in reality, there are people who give
really embarrassing magic names, right?

【Masamune】 As long as it's easy for the person
themselves to imagine, it's fine, right?
スキット 表情 レオン f 2

【Leon】 Yeah, but the other day there was someone
who was saying a really long name for an advanced
fire magic spell, and I almost burst out laughing.
スキット 表情 レオン f 3

【Leon】 You don't have time to chant during battle,
right?

【Masamune】 (I'm thinking of naming my advanced
fire magic spell 'Magical Flame Bullet', but is
this kind of lame...)

【Skeleton Head】 There used to be a lot of magic
like that in the past, but recently, there isn't
much, right?

【Skeleton Head】 As long as it's based on the magic
level and type, it's not a problem.
【Leon】 Magicians tend to use words like 'abyss'.
【Skeleton Head】 Ahaha...

【Masamune】 (I can't seem to get along with these
guys.)
スキット 終了

【Hiyo】 ...
スキット 表情 日和 f 3

【Hiyo】 (I won't give it a too fancy name from now
on, otherwise...)
スキット 終了
